01:07:23,853 --> 01:07:25,821
You know
that's not true.

756
01:07:25,855 --> 01:07:29,450
Nothing is ever your fault.
right. Harris?

757
01:07:29,492 --> 01:07:31,460
I'm not the one
wasting my life.

758
01:07:31,494 --> 01:07:33,894
