01:27:37,899 --> 01:27:39,560
Get in. Get in!

892
01:28:00,889 --> 01:28:04,085
Go!

893
01:28:05,393 --> 01:28:08,954
Go... go!

894
01:28:12,167 --> 01:28:14,328
Allison. Go!

895
01:28:24,346 --> 01:28:25,335
Go!

896
01:29:06,821 --> 01:29:09,051
Harris!

